{"tid":2103903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東莞上萬隻豬腳及內臟佈滿沙灘","createTime":"2020-07-11T13:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T17:46:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ba53cd99c6ec8e6cc4c0de8296c15c19d6a3e6","tid":2103903,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"中國東莞市虎門威遠島的沙灘上，竟在一夜之間出現大量豬腳以及動物內臟，畫面相當驚人，目前工作人員已經全力投入「清理豬腳」的工作，當地公安部門也開始進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，有網友發現東莞虎門威遠島接近虎門大橋的海灘上，竟然出現超大量的「豬腳、內臟」，因此迅速向媒體爆料。虎門海戰博物館的管理人員也向記者證實，昨（10）日晚上11點時發現海灘上出現零星的豬腳，沒想到隔天竟然發現更多豬腳以及內臟遍佈整個沙灘，初估光是豬腳數量就可能有上萬支。<br />\n<br />\n現場工作人員初估豬腳約有20噸，但已經差不多清理完畢，不過在該地附近的海岸也都出現了豬腳的蹤影。至於這批大量豬腳的來源以及被沖上岸的原因，則仍有待當地相關部門釐清。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3225481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3225481&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=9e1659fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3225481&h=c4e9305c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3225481</a>"},{"pid":"84b3347cd2869ba37375b4cf4c8a400a8a1c3903","tid":2103903,"uid":53666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"人腳混入"},{"pid":"450680a817fa63a7db54a1defcf44247eda94c45","tid":2103903,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"想去現場深呼吸一下"},{"pid":"44662b56433bf51efaa5d03b2553f438783ba21c","tid":2103903,"uid":188176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"之前非洲豬瘟大陸特登掉d豬落海飄去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bee87e3a65fe9ce38e12ada2a3dd09f6a8bb902","tid":2103903,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"『豬腳』<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"